            <title>[DERBY-3859] Reset the current role when EmbedPooledConnection creates a new logical connection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3859</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Similar to what happens to the current schema, the current role should be reset&lt;br/&gt;
when the EmbedPooledConnection creates a new logical connection, so that the current role, if set, is not inherited.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cf &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3690&quot; title=&quot;EmbedPooledConnection doesn&amp;#39;t reset schema when creating a new logical connection&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-3690&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-3690&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
